{"tid":2428091,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：提醒澳洲即使發出香港難民簽證 政治上都是開放給中國的","createTime":"2021-03-01T10:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T10:29:48.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"63f40b15787a0100c32b18f6fd105139c04451be","tid":2428091,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:00:13.000Z","msg":"美方籲釋放香港泛民人士 中方敦促美方停止干涉內政<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿布林肯譴責香港扣押並起訴泛民人士，呼籲立即釋放他們。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人汪文斌表示，堅定支持香港警方依法履職，維護國家安全和香港的安全與穩定，敦促美方停止以任何方式干涉香港事務。<br />\n<br />\n對於澳洲政府向香港居民批出難民庇護簽證的問題，汪文斌說，中方在涉港問題上的立場是一貫、明確的，香港是中國的香港，香港事務純屬中國內政，任何外國無權干涉，敦促澳方停止以任何方式干涉香港事務及中國內政，以免對中澳關係造成進一步損害。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578147-20210301.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578147-20210301.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt17Y5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=60204367\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578147-20210301.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=de8aacb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578147-20210301.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"119c4348eef0870d90ce9ec8ec32467b51fa950d","tid":2428091,"uid":41509,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"點解會屌澳洲，唔屌加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加拿大基本上係用錢買pr,夠錢讀幾年書就搞掂"},{"pid":"56a2d5f80ad6e6145af7f322ebff5fb4b346b95b","tid":2428091,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"119c4348eef0870d90ce9ec8ec32467b51fa950d","tid":2428091,"uid":41509,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"點解會屌澳洲，唔屌加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加拿大基本上係用錢買pr,夠錢讀幾年書就搞掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:04:21.000Z","msg":"中國因為慢慢周單野已經同加拿大半反臉，玩埋人質外交"},{"pid":"06574d8e3e52c7d9d83da952413700b80991b5c1","tid":2428091,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23936b42c2f374d758241a9bbac3d8c6238cf99","tid":2428091,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"119c4348eef0870d90ce9ec8ec32467b51fa950d","tid":2428091,"uid":41509,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"點解會屌澳洲，唔屌加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加拿大基本上係用錢買pr,夠錢讀幾年書就搞掂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:24:19.000Z","msg":"是但啦 小學雞係咁"},{"pid":"3e41562c0b65ca58222bac1d1f941107d7c737d1","tid":2428091,"uid":39872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:25:02.000Z","msg":"我宣佈習近平條命受到威脅中共係唔會收手"},{"pid":"9e3b801f8b03fb8f84d87f20eb2eb6668ebf7960","tid":2428091,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b23936b42c2f374d758241a9bbac3d8c6238cf99","tid":2428091,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"119c4348eef0870d90ce9ec8ec32467b51fa950d","tid":2428091,"uid":41509,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"點解會屌澳洲，唔屌加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加拿大基本上係用錢買pr,夠錢讀幾年書就搞掂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:24:19.000Z","msg":"是但啦 小學雞係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:29:48.000Z","msg":"澳洲好恰恰啲，支那買咁多澳洲嘢"}]}